description: Idle timers, warm pool, and concurrency tokens
alwaysApply: true
---

- Per-function config: `reserved_concurrency`, `idle_soft_ms`, `idle_hard_ms`, `pool_min`, `pool_max`.
- Acquire token → assign container (warm or cold) → release token when response posted.
- Soft idle: `docker stop`; Hard idle: `docker rm`.
- No reuse after Timeout/OOM/InitError.